      "content": "Your panic stems from the belief that this single failure erases your entire history, but great leaders have also faced massive obsolescence and started anew. While the immediate weight feels crushing, isolation often amplifies guilt, and speaking with a board mentor or legal advisor can reveal concrete paths to protecting others without confessing every sin. The future is not written in stone, even in the darkest moments, because even in times of great loss, people have found renewed purpose years later.",
      "source": "target",
