      "content": "but \"starting anew\" assumes there's anything left to start with. my life is tied to this. the debt, the legal stuff, the way people will talk about me at every dinner for the rest of my life. i'm just exhausted by the idea of even trying to survive this. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the shame is to just... make it stop. for good. it feels like the only honest way out.",
